{"tid":123784,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"沉左個姐姐船","createTime":"2017-02-17T05:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T07:48:44.000Z","uid":81264,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72e8b234787b256ed2709655c57b9b53f3620dbc","tid":123784,"uid":81264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"細路識左個大我八年既姐姐<br />\n佢係鐘意我但之前個陣我覺得年齡差太遠<br />\n加上小弟父母都係好傳統..我覺得煩..無乜將來咁就同佢講做朋友算<br />\n佢都講過話同我好似無將來..畢竟佢都30中<br />\n前排同佢攪左<br />\n攪完之後失哂控<br />\n佢問左好多次究竟我想點<br />\n但我都唔敢面對佢<br />\n因為我知我同佢將來會好難行<br />\n近排佢溝近條仔<br />\n佢話係溝黎為左唔再依賴我<br />\n我開始失控<br />\n佢叫我唔好咁自私<br />\n但佢次次同我講個條仔我就好失落<br />\n有冇人可以話我知我係米應該愈早抽身愈好<br />\n我feel到自己沉哂船..以家不斷幻想近同佢既將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點算呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d092376729c94acffd4cf28ff0aec6b64d0fbe2","tid":123784,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:38:04.000Z","msg":"米你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2f08736920a7aaf37254d568ce141979eefef6","tid":123784,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5a4895e09c08931d12a51c793d12441270d0256","tid":123784,"uid":2423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"你知唔知咩叫沉船呀 on9 仔"},{"pid":"6fa8a4382b235c70b87a5bfc454151e005a559f9","tid":123784,"uid":32114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"沉船？<br />\n你當自己係嫖客？定當對方係雞？"},{"pid":"07c980cf30ac6dc0e8bcfbb4dd9e6bbe499b0631","tid":123784,"uid":2423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>米你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n米你老母"},{"pid":"6f36ebb96757854a8821005af09a189ff42d46f6","t